attr.title: LISA: The Unbreakable
attr.desc: LISA: The Unbreakable is a Fangame set in the LISA Universe made by FXF
attr.desc_md: LISA: The Unbreakable is a Fangame set in the LISA Universe made by FXF.
attr.inst:
Download the game from Gamejolt, tested with Windows version. Copy the contents Lisa is dead folder to the gamedata folder.

Note: This game is not ideal for devices with low resolution displays and/or absent joysticks.
attr.inst_md:
Download the game from GameJolt (tested with Windows version). Copy the contents of the "Lisa is dead" folder to the gamedata folder.

**Note:** This game is not ideal for devices with low resolution displays and/or absent joysticks.
